 "cells": [

   "source": [
    "\n",
    "# Tutorial: Traj Segmentation \n",
    "\n",
    "**The following notebook illustrate the `TrajSegmentation` class.**\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "* Loading dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from IPython.display import SVG, display\n",
    "\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.tracking_data.tracking_data import TrackingConfig\n",
    "from megabouts.tracking_data.load_example import load_example_data\n",
    "from megabouts.tracking_data.tracking_data import FullTrackingData\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.traj_preprocessing import TrajPreprocessingConfig\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.traj_preprocessing import TrajPreprocessingResult\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.traj_preprocessing import TrajPreprocessing\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.tail_preprocessing import TailPreprocessingConfig\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.tail_preprocessing import TailPreprocessingResult\n",
    "from megabouts.preprocessing.tail_preprocessing import TailPreprocessing\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation_config import TailSegmentationConfig\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation_config import TrajSegmentationConfig\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation import TailSegmentation\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation import TrajSegmentation\n",
    "\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation import SegmentationFactory\n",
    "from megabouts.segmentation.segmentation import SegmentationResult"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Loading Data and Preprocessing"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "* TrackingConfig and TrackingData similar to [tutorial_Tail_Preprocessing](./tutorial_Tail_Preprocessing.ipynb)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_recording, fps, mm_per_unit = load_example_data('fulltracking_posture')\n",
    "\n",
    "tracking_cfg = TrackingConfig(fps=fps, tracking='full_tracking')\n",
    "\n",
    "head_x = df_recording['head_x'].values*mm_per_unit\n",
    "head_y = df_recording['head_y'].values*mm_per_unit\n",
    "head_yaw = df_recording['head_angle'].values\n",
    "tail_angle = df_recording.filter(like='tail_angle').values\n",
    "\n",
    "tracking_data = FullTrackingData.from_posture(head_x = head_x,\n",
    "                                              head_y = head_y,\n",
    "                                              head_yaw = head_yaw,\n",
    "                                              tail_angle = tail_angle)\n",
    "\n",
    "tail_preprocessing_cfg = TailPreprocessingConfig(fps=tracking_cfg.fps)\n",
    "\n",
    "tail_preprocessing_cfg = TailPreprocessingConfig(fps=tracking_cfg.fps,\n",
    "                                                 num_pcs=4,\n",
    "                                                 savgol_window_ms=15,\n",
    "                                                 tail_speed_filter_ms = 100,\n",
    "                                                 tail_speed_boxcar_filter_ms = 14\n",
    "                                                 )\n",
    "tail_df_input = tracking_data.tail_df\n",
    "tail = TailPreprocessing(tail_preprocessing_cfg).preprocess_tail_df(tail_df_input)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "traj_preprocessing_cfg = TrajPreprocessingConfig(fps=tracking_cfg.fps)\n",
    "traj_df_input = tracking_data.traj_df\n",
    "traj = TrajPreprocessing(traj_preprocessing_cfg).preprocess_traj_df(traj_df_input)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Segmentation using kinematic vigor"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "kinematic_vigor = traj.vigor\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "traj_segmentation_cfg = TrajSegmentationConfig(fps=tracking_cfg.fps,\n",
    "                                               peak_prominence=0.75,\n",
    "                                               peak_percentage=0.1\n",
    "                                               )\n",
    "segmentation_function = SegmentationFactory.get_segmenter(traj_segmentation_cfg)\n",
    "segments = segmentation_function.segment_from_traj(kinematic_vigor)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {
    "tags": [
     "hide-input"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1500x500 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig,ax = plt.subplots(2,1,figsize=(15,5),sharex=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "x = tracking_data._tail_angle[:,7]\n",
    "ax[0].plot(x)\n",
    "ax[0].plot(segments.onset, x[segments.onset], \"x\",color='green',label='onset')\n",
    "ax[0].plot(segments.offset, x[segments.offset], \"x\",color='red',label='offset')\n",
    "ax[0].set_ylim(-4,4)\n",
    "ax[0].legend()\n",
    "ax[0].set(title='trajectory segmentation',ylabel='angle (rad)',ylim=(-4,4))\n",
    "\n",
    "x = kinematic_vigor\n",
    "ax[1].plot(x)\n",
    "ax[1].plot(segments.onset, x[segments.onset], \"x\",color='green')\n",
    "ax[1].plot(segments.offset, x[segments.offset], \"x\",color='red')\n",
    "ax[1].set(ylabel='vigor (A.U)')\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "t = np.arange(tracking_data.T)/tracking_cfg.fps\n",
    "IdSt = np.random.randint(tracking_data.T)\n",
    "Duration = 10*tracking_cfg.fps\n",
    "ax[1].set_xlim(IdSt,IdSt+Duration)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Number of bouts as function of threshold:\n",
    "thresh_list = np.linspace(0.1,20,100)\n",
    "num_peaks = np.zeros_like(thresh_list)\n",
    "kinematic_vigor = traj.vigor\n",
    "\n",
    "for i,thresh in enumerate(thresh_list):\n",
    "    traj_segmentation_cfg = TrajSegmentationConfig(fps=tracking_cfg.fps,\n",
    "                                                   peak_prominence=thresh,\n",
    "                                                   peak_percentage=0.1)\n",
    "    segmentation_function = SegmentationFactory.get_segmenter(traj_segmentation_cfg)\n",
    "    segments = segmentation_function.segment_from_traj(kinematic_vigor)\n",
    "\n",
    "    num_peaks[i] = len(segments.onset)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {
    "tags": [
     "hide-input"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1500x400 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(15,4))\n",
    "plt.plot(thresh_list,num_peaks)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  }
